Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早飯要涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新婚家庭也就是這種感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最多也只是寄宿的  不是女婿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過本來就以女婿來想像就錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的話這麼想像的都是新娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始習慣這島了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這麼漂亮的盒子是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這是什麼盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴不知道手機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用這個的話應該能和遠方的人交談的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不能在這裡起到作用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…但是有事情的話  直接見面說不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊  說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃早飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:53.02,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有用的寄宿者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直認為不吃早飯是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從來這個島之後  為什麼能吃那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早飯是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好吃會沒有力氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打水啊  打家裡一天裡要用的量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有自來水管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  讓我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「滴水之恩當湧泉相報」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是爺爺的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼點算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連電氣  煤氣  自來水管都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是靠自給自足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是這種花力氣的活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對女孩來說太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有鈴和炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那  那  那個罐子是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的媽媽和婆婆很嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦著讓我一次就打完水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看凜這個樣子  她是島上第一大力士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上…第一…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:18.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不服輸）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說一下…我家早就過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子  要把我的水分點給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子還真愛逞強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…這點還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然丟下我  真無情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近  水要灑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命命是凜的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡凜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對行人是沒興趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:21.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{/fad(400,0)}（感覺到輸了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺  那有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被女孩所追趕的這種理所當然的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被這個島毒害的證據啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感謝你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把纏著姐姐的那些礙事的傢伙趕走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我家的姐姐出手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就不會就這樣簡單輕饒了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候我成為你的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用後腳跟…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣洗的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想幫鈴是很好的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想在不同文明的這個島上好好生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是實現不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然…小看了…家務活…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到…是這樣的…體力勞動…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為工作之後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是剛才行人所搬回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的大自然裡自給自足也很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  差不多該去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的份完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始是真正的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天一天也要好好加油  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…太小看了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了  開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  鈴是做什麼工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幫助那些忙碌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是什麼都做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙收割一下番薯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小靜  小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人說也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔番薯的話就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說在幼稚園的拔番薯大會上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都是挖的最多而受表揚的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是行人一個人的話絕對不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在體力上我也許有點比不上大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無論如何也不要太小看我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世上沒有絕對不行的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量方面我可是不會輸的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起拔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番…番薯  有這樣巨大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  今天有點小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說番薯的話  就該這麼小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在行人那邊有那麼小嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單是番薯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔這個  搬這個還真花體力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也想拜託幫下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把這些的毛…全部剪下來嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  快點做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人會來幫忙～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是羊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…其他的羊還是見過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島的動植物還真是微妙的有點奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說奇異呢…還是怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  還是不去在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  行人  要小心點剪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子生氣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…會群起而攻之的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  釣到了好大的一隻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釣這像魚一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人是第一次給牛擠奶?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣  度過了我漫長的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比捉迷藏還累
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃  千影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又坐著奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的是說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對著這樣英俊的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子可是有「鴨鴨」這樣出色的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快向鴨鴨道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那邊不是回家的方向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要去山裡采松茸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為前一陣子的雨   松茸正好可以吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不採  就要變大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是能吃的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經足夠大了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人你還是不要拔比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家拔起來的明明都那麼輕…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:49.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（偽松茸）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快點放開行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸長率  1.35到1.48倍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒素蔓延的速度  每秒240毫升	
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  偽松茸和蜜蜂蟄人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了人之後  自己也會乾枯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人也乾枯了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是松茸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個則是剛才襲擊行人的偽松茸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴  你們是怎麼分辨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是行人還沒習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫炸豬排告訴你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排  雖然你的心情是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我自己居然連松茸都分別不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為男人真是太丟臉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴  再告訴我多點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分辨真的和假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都好  告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會感覺到深黑的光澤  稍微有點酸的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深黑又有酸味是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深黑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有酸的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是白色光澤的  有著甜甜的味道的才是…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和剛才完全不同嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說怎樣分別的話  我以前都沒有想過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃還是只能憑藉野生的感覺來區分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野生的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為藏的很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但欺騙不了我•的•眼•睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙才是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在行人選到假的幾率到現在為止是100%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  行人認為「這個是假的」的話  這個就是真的松茸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根松茸從剛才開始就散發著味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吃了幾次之後我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的野生感在說這傢伙就是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的感覺是不正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  我所認為的這假松茸就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的松茸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找松茸對行人來說是不行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在行人面前  是不能說「絕對不行」的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「絕對不行」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這樣說的時侯  知道我會有多麼不甘心的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對  絕對  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行…絕對不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會輸給你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼  還沒完呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次…再來一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行…絕對不行…絕對不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把森林中的偽松茸全部打倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能猜不中到這種程度  某種意義上也是很厲害的才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:29.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{/fad(400,0)}（強者們所經歷的夢之痕跡）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有採到真的松茸 是不能存活在這個島上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別失落  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的鴨鴨也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光顧著給自己找食物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有起到作用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有作用…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想獨自待一會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反抗爸爸而離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果到頭來自己還是一個人什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是渺小的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且相比之下蔬菜也好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴她們也很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇著你了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找能作為好的木材的樹木
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是村裡第一的大力士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你很沒有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微有點討厭沒用的自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「男人在失落的時候最能容易地攻下」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那  那個呢  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:18:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我稱呼您為「公子」  是有深一層的意…意…意思的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就  就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女  女婿的意…意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公  公  公子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼害羞的事情說不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子  成為我的女婿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  兩個人在卿卿我我什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  難得正在高潮呢  居然來打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  行人  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流鼻血了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鼻血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  鼻血是鼻血啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候還流鼻血…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真不謹慎啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要強迫人家還真卑鄙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚯蚓！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別晃　別過來  別靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜受不了這種扭扭的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是像小孩呢  對蚯蚓還會害怕成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅…囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西快丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼如你所願  丟掉了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  雪乃  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係那麼好  不要管就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不是在害怕嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等  鴨鴨…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝  謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:20:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚯蚓輕輕鬆鬆地就扔飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子差不多都喜歡蟲啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以完全不害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是這樣說  但也是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要說的話 看到那麼大的也在發抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  鈴的話要更加厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都能做  被大家所依賴著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作做了那麼多  一句怨言都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此相比的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如雪乃說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全起不到作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鈴救了好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了那麼多的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報恩什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為寄宿的我真是丟臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報恩的話已經做得足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個島只有我是孤獨一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在工作結束之後  看著大家一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣和行人能一起回家  聊天  吃飯  一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和行人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就已經很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像  有了家人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和炸豬排一起  也很高興的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
